	Support input shapes:  (#331070)
	
	* gdk/gdk.symbols: 
	* gdk/gdkdisplay.h: 
	* gdk/gdkwindow.h: 
	* gdk/x11/gdkdisplay-x11.c (gdk_display_supports_shapes) 
	(gdk_display_supports_input_shapes): Functions to determine
	if a display supports shaped windows or input shapes.

